{"LEFT":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to that side of the body in man on which the muscular action of the limbs is usually weaker than on the other side; -- opposed to right, when used in reference to a part of the body; as, the left ear.","pos":""}],"LEFT-HAND":[{"def":"Situated on the left; nearer the left hand than the right; as, the left-hand side; the left-hand road.","pos":""}],"LEFT-HANDED":[{"def":"The state or quality of being left-handed; awkwardness.","pos":""}],"LEFT-OFF":[{"def":"Laid a side; cast-off.","pos":""}],"LEFTWARD":[{"def":"Toward or on the left side.","pos":""}]}